{
  "id": "class_0004",
  "name": "Pitch-Stained Border Mage",
  "title_completion": "a Pitch-Stained Border Mage",
  "flavor_text": "They say the wall was built to keep things out, but she learned long ago that the most dangerous things are already on the inside. She moves through checkpoints like smoke through iron bars, leaving trails of burning pitch and brine that linger long after she's gone. The guards never see her cross \u2014 only the smoldering evidence that she did.",
